    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the<strong> carrot ribbons</strong>, <strong>cucumber matchsticks</strong>,<strong> sliced shallot</strong>, <strong>salad</strong>, <strong>sesame croutons</strong> and most of the <strong>chopped mint </strong>and <strong>chopped coriander </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) to the hoisin dressing and give it a gentle mix up – this is your <strong>bánh mì-style salad</strong></p>",
